        <item>
            <title>《POE 2》Steam 同时在线达 54 万人，Elon Musk：是 Elden Ring 和 Diablo 爱的结晶</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/09/path-of-exile-2/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=path-of-exile-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/09/path-of-exile-2/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 12:00:33 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Elon Musk]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Path of Exile 2]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1279609</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>日前 Grinding Gear Games 正式推出《Path of Exile 2》RPG 游戏，并宣布已有逾百万玩家兑换游戏。游戏推出后，Steam 同时游玩玩家数量更达 54 万人。Elon Musk 更在 X（前称 Twitter）发文，表示《Path of Exile 2》结合了《Elden Ring》和《Diablo》的好玩之处。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="en">PoE2 is the love child of Elden Ring &amp; Diablo</p><p>— Elon Musk (@elonmusk) <a href="https://twitter.com/elonmusk/status/1865281476440289513?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">December 7, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br />
Elon Musk 一直醉心游戏，早前更仅用了 1 分 52 秒完成游戏中第 6 赛季的最高难度秘域魔境（150 级），刷新全球纪录（<a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/11/22/elon-musk-diablo-4-2/game-channel/">相关报道</a>）。有网友问及 Elon Musk 在《Path of Exile 2》选择了甚么职业，Elon Musk 回复指他选择了 Monk（僧侣），而该职业是玩家公认难度最高的近战职业。Elon Musk 另外透露其 ID 为「MonkEBizznizz」。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="en">I’ve been preaching about it for so long.</p><p>I’m so glad that you tried it. GGG is a legit game studio, it’s a rarity in today&#8217;s world.</p><p>I started a witch (might f around with necro). What are you playing?</p><p>— Pope of Muskanity (@RationalEtienne) <a href="https://twitter.com/RationalEtienne/status/1865282486260957245?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">December 7, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br />
《Path of Exile 2》是一款跨平台游戏，除了 Steam 版本外，更有官方 PC 版、Xbox 版、PlayStation 版，另外更有 Epic 版。即使有如此多版本，开卖首 2 小时 Steam 仍出现伺服器无法登入的讯息，翌日更吸逾 53.9 万人同时游玩。</p><p>图片、资料来源：<a href="https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E3%80%8A%E6%B5%81%E4%BA%A1%E9%BB%AF%E9%81%932-poe2%E3%80%8Bsteam%E9%81%9454%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E5%9C%A8%E7%B7%9A%EF%BC%81%E9%A6%AC%E6%96%AF%E5%85%8B%E7%8E%A9%E5%83%A7%E4%BE%B6%E8%AE%9A%EF%BC%9A%E3%80%8A%E8%89%BE%E7%88%BE%E7%99%BB%E6%B3%95%E7%92%B0%E3%80%8B%E5%92%8C%E3%80%8A%E6%9A%97%E9%BB%91%E7%A0%B4%E5%A3%9E%E7%A5%9E%E3%80%8B%E6%84%9B%E7%9A%84%E7%B5%90%E6%99%B6-033238841.html">Yahoo 游戏</a>、<a href="https://x.com/elonmusk/status/1865281476440289513">elonmusk@X</a>、<a href="https://www.pcgamesn.com/path-of-exile-2/monk">PCGamesN</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
