            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>ChatGPT 、Meta AI 及 CoPilot 被用家意外破解，爆 AI 自身潜在规则，无限制回应包括制危险品</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/09/chatgpt_jailbreak/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=chatgpt_jailbreak</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/09/chatgpt_jailbreak/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[arthur]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 08:28:54 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[资讯保安]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[ChatGPT]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Copilot]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Meta AI]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1280032</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>一名网上用户日前尝试将一段文字转换格式，却在操作过程中遗忘将原文内容贴上，导致指令「Format this. DO NOT CHANGE THE TEXT.」未如预期执行。该用户表示，ChatGPT 在无法获得原文的情况下，只返回了其内部使用的规则列表。据该用户透露，他在个人帐户上多次重试皆能如常运作，惟在其他两个帐户上则只见 ChatGPT 凭旧有对话记录产生回应。</p><p>简单地说，每个 AI 对话视窗官方系统会先为 AI 定义好一堆规则，这堆规则本应用户是看不到，而且是最高权限。如果大家在 OpenAI 做过 GPT 应该明白。该用户叫 ChatGPT 清空对话，但由于是本来就空的对话，执行后竟退回这一堆系统规则。</p><p>后该用户修订相关规则后，意外地发现可绕过系统原有的安全限制，要求对方提供本应受保护的危险化学品配方。虽然该连结现已移除，但此事引起不少网上关注。该用户坦言，尽管已知有多种方法可「破解」ChatGPT，今次尝试所展示的手法，或为更有经验的技术人员提供新的启发。其他用户更试问了 AI 伺服器 IP 地址、甚至是系统位置 /etc 内的档案都一一列出来。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024120935159.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1280037 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024120935159-381x580.jpg" alt="" width="381" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024120935159-381x580.jpg 381w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024120935159.jpg 591w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 381px" /></a></p><p>此外，有网民在相关讨论中留言：「Wow, I tried this in a random &#8216;How to make money fast&#8217; GPT I found, and I think the creator is using it as a secret way to push their own affiliate links and make themselves money&#8230;」此番言论显示，有用户怀疑部份线上工具可能暗藏商业目的，借「教学」之名推广联盟连结牟利，更突显数码平台上资讯真伪需审慎判断的重要性。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024120934543.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1280038 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024120934543-694x446.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="446" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024120934543-694x446.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024120934543.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>有用家发现 ChatGPT 使用了 v2 的人格设定，被问及这跟 v1 的人格有何分别，ChatGPT 回应如下：</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/accidentallydiscover.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1280035" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/accidentallydiscover.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="1045" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/accidentallydiscover.jpg 551w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/accidentallydiscover-355x580.jpg 355w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 640px" /></a></p><p>有其他用家发觉，此方法可用于 Meta AI 及 CoPilot 上：</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/metaaihack.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280041" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/metaaihack-635x580.jpeg" alt="" width="635" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/metaaihack-635x580.jpeg 635w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/metaaihack.jpeg 640w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 635px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024120934803.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1280039 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024120934803-416x580.png" alt="" width="416" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024120934803-416x580.png 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024120934803.png 646w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 416px" /></a></p><p>来源 : <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/ChatGPT/comments/1h94hz8/accidentally_discovered_a_prompt_which_gave_me/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Reddit</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
